    <item>
      <title>反垄断问题加剧，Google Play 应用商店收入面临冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/google-play-must-allow-rival-android-app-stores-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官裁定，Alphabet Inc. 必须取消禁止开发商建立与 Google Play Store 竞争的竞争市场和计费系统的限制，这将颠覆这家搜索巨头在利润丰厚的 Android 应用市场的主导地位，并可能削弱其收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/google-play-must-allow-rival-android-app-stores-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
